short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds a graphical timeline to GitHub Milestones

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A visual timeline based on GitHub Milestone due dates will be added to the top of the Milestones pages of GitHub projects along with a green dot indicating the current date.
